#

Caramelized Apple Pancakes

30 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyEggsGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSweetEasy

Description

Deliciously fluffy pancakes topped with sweet and buttery caramelized apples for a comforting breakfast treat.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 1
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • baking powder: 2 teaspoons
  • apples: 2
  • brown sugar: 3 tablespoons
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
